metadata.name: 1st connection with Viberium
metadata.description:
The beginning of a journey is always a special exciting mood. The anticipation of adventure and a slight jitters from the unknown. Going to Viberium, one thing should be especially remembered: every move you make here, every impulse will lead you to different results. 
Collect tokens of different energy: dark, light or neutral and move through the Viberium maze! 
And one day we will meet there!

*The owner of this item will receive an original png image 3000 x 3000 px and the opportunity to participate in the drawing of exclusive NFT tokens in future.
